title: ISSS626-GAA
text: Welcome to ISSS626 - Geospatial Analytics and Applications. In this website you will find my coursework prepared for this course.

title: Hands-on Exercise 1
text:
The code chunk below uses p_load() of pacman package to check if tidyverse packages are installed in the computer. If they are, they will be launched into R.

pacman::p_load(tidyverse)





listings_data <- read_csv("data/aspatial/listings.csv")
